<body class="show">
<div class="review-background-image">
  <%= video_tag "show_video.mp4", autoplay: true, muted: true, loop: true, class: "background-show" %>
  <div class="reviewsection">
    <h1> Reviews of <%=@pub.name %>: </h1>
    <% @pub.reviews.each do |review| %>
      <div>
        <% review.rating.times do %>
          <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <% end %>
        <p class="mb-0"><%= review.comment %></p>
      </div>
      <hr>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>


<ul>
  <li class="booking-card" style="background-image: url(https://d1e00ek4ebabms.cloudfront.net/production/8669b7f0-b3bb-4c07-ad74-88af722d110b.jpg)">
    <div class="book-container">

      <div class="content">
        <button class="btn" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal">Add to Pub Crawl </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="informations-container">
      <h2 class="title"><%= @pub.name %> </h2>
      <p class="sub-title">An excellent pub for your pub crawl!</p>
      <p class="price"><svg class="icon" style="width:24px;height:24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
    <path fill="currentColor" d="M3,6H21V18H3V6M12,9A3,3 0 0,1 15,12A3,3 0 0,1 12,15A3,3 0 0,1 9,12A3,3 0 0,1 12,9M7,8A2,2 0 0,1 5,10V14A2,2 0 0,1 7,16H17A2,2 0 0,1 19,14V10A2,2 0 0,1 17,8H7Z" />
      Hover for more information</svg></p>
        <div class="more-information">
          <div class="info-and-date-container">
            <div class="box info">
              <svg class="icon" style="width:24px;height:24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path fill="currentColor" d="M11,9H13V7H11M12,20C7.59,20 4,16.41 4,12C4,7.59 7.59,4 12,4C16.41,4 20,7.59 20,12C20,16.41 16.41,20 12,20M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M11,17H13V11H11V17Z" />
      </svg>
              <p>May cause too good of a time</p>
            </div>
            <div class="box date">
              <svg class="icon" style="width:24px;height:24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path fill="currentColor" d="M19,19H5V8H19M16,1V3H8V1H6V3H5C3.89,3 3,3.89 3,5V19A2,2 0 0,0 5,21H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,19V5C21,3.89 20.1,3 19,3H18V1M17,12H12V17H17V12Z" />
      </svg>
              <p>Closes 12am</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="disclaimer">A bar stool plays pinochle with a discusting Long Trail Ale. A micro brew over the Hops Alligator Ale befriends some Yuengling about the keg. Any Ipswich Ale can sanitize a whacked Pilsner, but it takes a real customer to negotiate a prenuptial agreement with the Miller. If another Budweiser Select trades baseball cards with a Sam Adams around the Octoberfest, then an ESB prays. If the raspy Pilsner Urquell negotiates a prenuptial agreement with the salty Sam Adams, then a plowed Budweiser dies.</p>
          </div>
    </div>
  </li>
</body>



<!-- Modal -->
 <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Add Pub to Pub Crawl</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
       <%= simple_form_for [@pub, @stop] do |f| %>
        <%= f.association :pub_crawl, collection: PubCrawl.all, prompt: "Select a Pub Crawl" %>
        <%= f.submit "Save Changes", class:"btn btn-primary"%>
       <% end %>

      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
      </div>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>

<div class="review-container">
  <div class="review-cards">
    <div class="review-card">
      <%# <% @reviews.each do |review|
          %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
